            "value": "NOTE",
            "note": "Use this class to describe an election event that is referenced or linked to a political advertisement. When a political advertisement has a clear and substantial link to an election, the title, level, and date of the election must be disclosed in the transparency notice as required by Article 12(1)(g) of Regulation (EU) 2024/900 and Annex II, Template 3, point 9 of Implementing Regulation (EU) 2025/1410. The level must be indicated as EU, national, regional, or local."
          }
