          "en": "Use this class to describe a legislative or regulatory initiative that is referenced or promoted by a political advertisement. When a political advertisement has a clear and substantial link to a legislative or regulatory initiative, the title and level of the initiative must be disclosed in the transparency notice under Article 12(1)(g) of Regulation (EU) 2024/900 and Annex II, Template 3, point 9 of Implementing Regulation (EU) 2025/1410. The title may be shortened."
        },
        "ap-label-en": {
          "en": "Initiative"
        },
        "ap-definition-en": {
          "en": "A project,program,or organised effort undertaken to achieve specific objectives, often in a political, legislative, or public context."
