      "name": "homepage",
      "inpackage": "OTHER_PACKAGE",
      "ap-definition-en": {
        "en": "The website of the Public Event."
      },
      "usage": {
        "en": "Provide the URL of the official website of the public event. For elections or referendums linked to a political advertisement, this should link to official information about the modalities for participation, as required by Article 12(1)(h) of Regulation (EU) 2024/900 and Annex II, Template 3, point 10 of Implementing Regulation (EU) 2025/1410."
